---
title: Caribbean Prawn Curry & Garlic Rice with Pineapple-Avocado Salsa & Fresh Chilli
description: Bring the tropics to your table with this Caribbean curry! With tender, flaky prawn and bold spices, it’s a flavour feast that’s sure to satisfy. Serve it over fragrant garlic rice and top with a zesty pineapple salsa and fresh chilli for a sweet and spicy kick. It’s a vacation in every bite!
